Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.53,0:38:26.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fs24\1c}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.81,0:38:28.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桑迪 我爱你 兄弟\N{\fs24\1c}Santi, I love you, brother.
