Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.92,0:38:34.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你 桑迪\N{\fs24\1c}I love you, Santi.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.59,0:38:36.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fs24\1c}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.58,0:38:37.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 怎么回事\N{\fs24\1c}Wait, what's happening?
