Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.79,0:38:47.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-莱顿 -你去哪\N{\fs24\1c}- Layton. - Where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.69,0:38:48.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱顿\N{\fs24\1c}Layton!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.11,0:38:49.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别走\N{\fs24\1c}Don't walk away!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.40,0:39:18.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关掉\N{\fs24\1c}Go now!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.42,0:39:51.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按住 按住 保持稳定\N{\fs24\1c}Get ahold of that. Get ahold of that. Keep it steady.
