Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.83,0:40:46.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的莱拉\N{\fs24\1c}My Lilah.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.05,0:40:57.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,降速 迈尔斯 还要再降速\N{\fs24\1c}Reduce speed, Miles. Take off even more.
