Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.99,0:41:20.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有我在\N{\fs24\1c}I gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.41,0:41:31.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们做到了\N{\fs24\1c}We did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.59,0:41:37.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好样的 工程师\N{\fs24\1c}Good job, Engineer.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.04,0:41:52.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你早知道我得丢下他们\N{\fs24\1c}You knew I'd have to cut them.
